{"tid":918100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平：寧死獄中不認罪","createTime":"2018-11-27T02:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T04:44:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"98475ae78f5c950cec53b2ce54582dc507475363","tid":918100,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181127/large/27la5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F27la5p6.jpg&h=dcfe9d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【《蘋果》記者陳建平紐約直擊】民政事務局前局長何志平涉貪案，經歷一年繁複司法程序後，在美國時間昨早上10時（香港時間昨晚上11時）終開始正式審訊，並將選出陪審團。在美國還柙逾一年的何志平至今拒認罪，聲稱寧死獄中也絕不屈服。法官早前預計案件審訊需時約四至六星期。根據法例，若何的八項控罪全部成立，最高可被判囚85年。<br />\n<br />\n罪成可判囚85年<br />\n<br />\n69歲的何志平去年11月18日在美國紐約被捕，隨即被司法部控告何五項串謀違反及違反《海外反腐敗法》及三項洗錢罪。控罪指2014年至2017年間，作為中華能源基金會秘書長的何，為替其幕後金主中國華信能源公司換取生意上的好處，先後賄賂多名非洲政要。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，何志平在另一被告、塞內加爾前外長加迪奧的協助下賄賂乍得總統；另外又涉嫌向烏干達的外長及總統提供利益。案件涉及賄款達290萬美元，當中包括2015年由香港、經紐約銀行分別匯款到加迪奧的杜拜戶口及烏干達外長的戶口，另外同年又帶同200萬美元現金贈乍得總統。<br />\n<br />\n根據何早前與外界接觸的通話及電郵紀錄，何曾稱自己是被利用去抓「大老虎」，又說自己寧死在獄中也不會屈服。<br />\n<br />\n對何不利的因素是，加迪奧早前已與司法部簽署協議，轉為控方證人以換取撤銷所有控罪，他將會作供指控何志平賄賂。若何的八項控罪全部罪成，而刑期又分期執行，他最多可被判監85年及罰款港幣4,524萬元。<br />\n<br />\n由何志平被捕至今，記者現場所見，其家人從未赴法院旁聽支持，只見辯方律師團隊為他奔走，反而華信能源公司曾派代表出席部份聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181127/20555570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F20555570&d=kPlvPdLcVkc%2Fw3cbopP%2FZkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8b1d3366\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F20555570&h=6b344fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181127/20555570</a>"},{"pid":"af8c35ede576db61c508b0081fd5e1870f081e2e","tid":918100,"uid":143499,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EizgPQe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEizgPQe.jpg&h=ea666a7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2597627495e467a9ecf4d9fbd6f80a8aca0a44f0","tid":918100,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"人質在故土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccfd11748e64b680f94b2cab38a17bbb25070e2","tid":918100,"uid":66381,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"何同志為國捐軀，香港政府欠何同志一個浩園位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d1b5d04b5641cc0d4d533ce01e0be580dccb5a","tid":918100,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:46:18.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"58ebf0dea7cb983466499f29a73cf66cb18d3332","tid":918100,"uid":60341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"佢啲家人喺哂邊？<br />\n喺中國俾人要脅？"},{"pid":"13b488561e37e9229f04101cceec014f9b6ce633","tid":918100,"uid":39872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"58ebf0dea7cb983466499f29a73cf66cb18d3332","tid":918100,"uid":60341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"佢啲家人喺哂邊？<br />\n喺中國俾人要脅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"講得出呢句就係屋企人畀脅持住<br />\n為保家人平安，佢別無選擇"},{"pid":"5ef79cd59f84330cad6b380d585a7cabc40d2298","tid":918100,"uid":54264,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/S1oD8lc0rfo/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FS1oD8lc0rfo%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=f2aba45e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00f869792ce8107567db48607e8897ba3358eb7c","tid":918100,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13b488561e37e9229f04101cceec014f9b6ce63