/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0208685c3bd69c17e4f42f81d9a6fbedde49330","tid":918100,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:31:42.000Z","msg":"咁你去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf8344d85953888292e601cba380368e8ac120e","tid":918100,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acfd05f660a24951661e7a5caaba05bf760889c","tid":918100,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"醒目,出到來應該即比人殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}